    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Create a `Painter` object.\r\n2. Add methods to paint a line to the cone\r\n\t- **Hint:** Use your pseudocode on the activity guide for Task 1: A to D.\r\n    \r\n---\r\n###AI Tutor Support\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure how to paint a line?**]\r\nAsk AI: \r\n- How do I make the Painter paint and move a certain number of steps?\r\n- How do I make the Painter turn in the right direction?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Getting an error message?**]\r\nAsk AI:\r\n- What does this error message mean: *Painter.paint() missing 1 required positional argument: 'color'*?\r\n- Why does it say: *There is no more paint in the painter's bucket*?\r\n:::\r\n",
